room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Orlando in Orlando
review: What an awesome experience! Played Mission: Mars and escaped - it is amazing! Management here is great too - we had an issue with an offer and they stepped up and took care of us. Great customer experience all around, highly recommend! About to do our second one in an hour.

room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Orlando in Orlando
review: Mission to Mars was so fun! It's so worth it, don't think twice about booking this for your family. We talked about it all the next day. Teenagers and adults worked to solve and we did escape but it was super fun!

room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Orlando in Orlando
review: Lots of fun! Time flew by and we Escaped Mars with minutes to spare!

room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Orlando in Orlando
review: I have played every game and mission to mars was a different but fun change of pace. Still hands down the best escape game out there.

room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Orlando in Orlando
review: We did the Mission Mars and had a blast. There were a total of nine of us in the room and it was very well decorated. Unfortunately we couldn't do the other four rooms here as we had already did them at their Austin TX. location. Would highly recommend.
